<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">Small,<sp/>thin<sp/>anti-aliased<sp/>fonts<sp/>are<sp/>typically<sp/>benefiting<sp/>a<sp/>lots<sp/>from<sp/>Freetype&apos;s<sp/>hinting:</highlight></codeline>
